290
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:07,640
Ha Jin. Ha Kyung.

291
00:20:07,779 --> 00:20:09,349
My gosh, what is this about?

292
00:20:09,349 --> 00:20:11,849
It must have hurt so much.

293
00:20:11,849 --> 00:20:13,519
Are you sure it's okay
to get discharged already?

294
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:16,720
You should get all the treatment
you can at the hospital.

295
00:20:16,720 --> 00:20:18,819
There's nothing to treat here.

296
00:20:18,819 --> 00:20:20,160
I'm all better now.

297
00:20:22,289 --> 00:20:24,730
After hearing the news,

298
00:20:24,730 --> 00:20:26,200
my hands were shaking.

299
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:28,730
I don't even know how I drove here.

300
00:20:29,170 --> 00:20:30,769
Ms. Park, let's sit down.

301
00:20:31,900 --> 00:20:33,970
At this rate,
you might faint before we do.

302
00:20:33,970 --> 00:20:36,339
Sit down and calm down.

303
00:20:40,210 --> 00:20:42,250
Ha Jin. Ha Kyung.

304
00:20:42,250 --> 00:20:45,750
Let's officially request the police
to investigate the stalker.

305
00:20:46,019 --> 00:20:48,349
It's not the time to worry
about your image right now.

306
00:20:48,349 --> 00:20:50,650
Who knows
what that jerk would try next?

307
00:20:50,650 --> 00:20:52,490
I agree with you.

308
00:20:52,490 --> 00:20:54,930
On my way here,
I talked to our lawyer.

309
00:20:54,930 --> 00:20:56,829
The lawyer says it's better...

310
00:20:56,829 --> 00:21:00,200
to report the break-in incident
at home and this attack together.

311
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:02,470
Then, what about the letters
Anchor Lee received?

312
00:21:02,470 --> 00:21:05,900
Those letters will be hard to be
considered as criminal conduct.

313
00:21:05,900 --> 00:21:08,269
It might just end up
piquing people's curiosity,

314
00:21:08,269 --> 00:21:10,009
so the lawyer advises
not to share that.

315
00:21:10,009 --> 00:21:11,609
And I agree.

316
00:21:11,710 --> 00:21:15,150
And I feel bad
in case this affects Anchor Lee.

317
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:19,279
Not disclosing the letters
might be better.

318
00:21:19,279 --> 00:21:21,819
Yes. Let's report this
as soon as possible...

319
00:21:21,819 --> 00:21:23,190
and catch that stalker first.

320
00:21:23,190 --> 00:21:25,059
Once I catch that stalker,

321
00:21:25,059 --> 00:21:27,920
I'll break his wrists, so he never
does something like this again.

322
00:21:27,920 --> 00:21:30,230
Ms. Park, leave that to me.

323
00:21:30,230 --> 00:21:31,230
Yes.

324
00:21:31,329 --> 00:21:33,630
So Ha Jin, don't worry about this.

325
00:21:33,630 --> 00:21:35,769
Just take care of yourself
and trust us.

326
00:21:35,769 --> 00:21:37,069
Okay?

327
00:21:37,069 --> 00:21:38,170
I will.

328
00:21:43,769 --> 00:21:47,980
Do you really like
that woman, Yeo Ha Jin?

329
00:21:49,410 --> 00:21:51,079
Don't you feel bad for Seo Yeon?

330
00:21:53,480 --> 00:21:55,390
But you killed Seo Yeon.

331
00:21:56,150 --> 00:21:57,750
And now, what do you think...

332
00:21:59,089 --> 00:22:01,059
you're doing with her friend?

333
00:22:40,930 --> 00:22:42,329
Yes. Hello?

334
00:22:42,970 --> 00:22:45,940
It's me. Is it a bad time to talk?

335
00:22:46,839 --> 00:22:48,269
I just wanted to let you know...

336
00:22:49,039 --> 00:22:50,539
that Ms. Park
suggested officially...

337
00:22:50,539 --> 00:22:52,009
requesting the police
to investigate.

338
00:22:52,009 --> 00:22:53,539
To report my stalker.

339
00:22:54,309 --> 00:22:55,480
I see. Yes.

340
00:22:56,549 --> 00:22:59,380
Given the turn of events now,
I think it's better too.

341
00:23:00,150 --> 00:23:02,589
The media will probably
publish a lot of articles on this.

342
00:23:03,619 --> 00:23:04,859
Probably, right?

343
00:23:04,859 --> 00:23:06,519
Be extra careful for the time being.

344
00:23:07,359 --> 00:23:09,559
Ask the police to protect you.

345
00:23:09,930 --> 00:23:11,599
And have bodyguards accompany you.

346
00:23:12,130 --> 00:23:13,500
Okay.

347
00:23:15,730 --> 00:23:18,740
I'm sorry that
I'm not much of a help to you.

348
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:21,269
You are such a big help. I mean it.

349
00:23:21,269 --> 00:23:22,970
Stop saying stuff like that.

350
00:23:23,809 --> 00:23:26,180
I'm not the only one in danger.
You're also in danger.

351
00:23:26,180 --> 00:23:27,980
Be careful, okay?

352
00:23:31,309 --> 00:23:34,519
By the way, you don't sound good.

353
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:36,019
Are you sick?

354
00:23:36,619 --> 00:23:38,019
No. I'm fine.

355
00:23:40,420 --> 00:23:42,190
Rest up. I'll call you again.

356
00:24:13,059 --> 00:24:14,059
(I'm always watching you.)

357
00:24:14,220 --> 00:24:15,230
(You're mine, Ha Jin.)

358
00:24:15,230 --> 00:24:16,329
(I want to make you happy.)

359
00:24:18,900 --> 00:24:22,329
