384
00:25:29,599 --> 00:25:31,000
So let's take this chance...

385
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:34,140
to change the idea people have
about stalking and stalkers.

386
00:25:34,940 --> 00:25:37,940
I think that could
help out Ha Jin a little too.

387
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:41,380
I know what you mean
