the stalker's punishment.

394
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:02,829
You have a point too.
I understand what you mean.

395
00:26:03,700 --> 00:26:08,039
Anyway, if you need anything,
let me know whenever.

396
00:26:08,369 --> 00:26:09,740
Yes, thank you.

397
00:26:09,740 --> 00:26:11,680
Okay. You can go now.

